@startuml
actor User
participant Frontend
participant "Meal API" as API
database PostgreSQL
participant "Statistics API" as StatAPI

User -> Frontend: Them bua an
Frontend -> API: POST /api/meals
API -> PostgreSQL: insert meal
API -> PostgreSQL: upsert daily_nutrition
API --> Frontend: meal created
Frontend -> StatAPI: GET /api/statistics/daily
StatAPI -> PostgreSQL: query nutrition
StatAPI --> Frontend: daily stats
@enduml
